window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tamlin Ashowan has troubled his family for years. Between the fearfulness of his magic and his refusal to share exactly what it does, his loving parents and sister don’t know how best to guide him. Tam, on the other hand, insists he doesn’t need any assistance. Despite ignoring his magic and possessing a preference for remaining locked up in his room with a good book, Tam is determined to play his role as the heir to his dukedom to the best of his ability. But being the son of Finlay Ashowan, the famous hero of Daxaria, his life is prone to chaos.</p> <p>Will a new assistant, who has even more secrets than Tam himself, be able to help navigate Tam's endless responsibilities? Will all chaos break out thanks to the unstable kingdom of Zinfera? And lastly, can Tam handle everything without having to use his magical power, or will he be pushed to new limits as his fate rushes to meet him?</p> <p>Find the answer to these questions and more in the new trilogy set in the same universe as The House Witch series, <i>The Princess of Potential</i>, and The Burning Witch series. There's no need to listen to the previous books to enjoy the new, fun adventure. Feel free to jump right in!</p>"; 
